 Famous Nollywood actor and Yoruba voice-over artiste, Lekan Olaleye shocks many when he admits that he has never spoken a foreign language to his seven-month-old son. Lekan made this revelation following a video he shared online. The footage captured a special moment he had with his son. Lekan Olaleye, in the video, was seen addressing his son in Yoruba langue. Ayomide Adegboye, Karen Igho, Foluke Daramola, Adekunle Rasheed, DJ Spicey, to mention, but few reacted to the video with lovely comments.  Another fan of the actor who reacted to the video queried him for speaking Yoruba to his son, urging him to speak English. He wrote: Timba Mu O Koh Baba Osoyinbo Nah In response, Lekan Olaleye admitted that he has never addressed his son in English sin he was born. lekan_kingkong: @oladipsoflife 1 Oyinbo I never speak to am since. E go learn am for school Watch video below:   A post shared by Olalekan Olaleye {Agba Inaki} (@lekan_kingkong) 